### =====================================================================
### Media API  (base route: api/media/)
### NOTE: Create is multipart/form-data (file upload). TagMedia: 101 Image, 102 Profile
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Create - upload a file (multipart). Replace the path after < with a real file.
POST {{host}}/api/media/Create
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ApiKey"

{{apiKey}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Token"

{{token}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Tag1"

101
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ProductId"

00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Title"

Sample image
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="File"; filename="sample.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### Read
POST {{host}}/api/media/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "tags": [101],
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1
}

### Update - metadata + attach to entity
POST {{host}}/api/media/Update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "title": "Updated title",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete
POST {{host}}/api/media/Delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### DeleteRange
POST {{host}}/api/media/DeleteRange
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "ids": ["00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001", "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"]
}

### Download (GET, query param)
GET {{host}}/api/media/Download?filePath=Media/sample.png
